OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRecord alcohol deaths from 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpandemic drinking          
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A record number of people died from    
OL,6, alcohol last year, which is likely to  
OL,7, be the result of increased drinking    
OL,8, during the pandemic, according to the  
OL,9, Office for National Statistics.        
OL,11,FThere were 9,641 deaths in the UK in   
OL,12,F2021, compared to 7,565 in 2019 - a 27%
OL,13,Fincrease.                              
OL,15,FThe ONS says people who were already   
OL,16,Fbig drinkers before the pandemic drank 
OL,17,Fmore during the Covid years.           
OL,19,FCharity Drinkaware said the numbers    
OL,20,Fwere "devastating" and "unacceptable". 
